citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:25- 10:05
AM on 06/02/2016.
Inspector arrived at a closed gate, honked GOV horn and called out for licensee with no response, inspector called
the listed number and left message.
